The paper discusses the detection of fraudulent activity in video ads, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms to detect fake views, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the need for independent tools to monitor and audit the fidelity of video hosting portals, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
